<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.app/weibo/user/2831150640" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>深圳卫健委的微博 - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>i@diygod.me (DIYgod)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.600.600.180/a8bfee30ly8hp22ftggynj20go0gomyy.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1717672669&amp;ssig=eLyGq8dR6o</url><title>深圳卫健委的微博</title><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 08:17:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>180</ttl><item><title>【[并不简单]近视能恢复？假的！】传言称，近视也能被治愈；戴眼镜近视度数会越来越深；小时候近视没关系，大不了成年后做近视手术……今天，#2024全国爱眼日#，...</title><description>【&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[并不简单]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;近视能恢复？假的！】传言称，近视也能被治愈；戴眼镜近视度数会越来越深；小时候近视没关系，大不了成年后做近视手术……今天，&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%232024%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%88%B1%E7%9C%BC%E6%97%A5%23&amp;amp;extparam=%232024%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%88%B1%E7%9C%BC%E6%97%A5%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#2024全国爱眼日#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;，关于近视这6个谣言，阿卫必须狠狠撕碎！&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫来辟谣#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（健康中国） &lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hqfpfc3ptoj20u01hcwov.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;n